701538f-a.title: Bronx: Odell Street - St. Raymond Avenue
701538f-a.text:
Odell Street, north from St. haymond Avenue. On the right are
buildings of the Bronx Gas and Electric Company. Part of this
area, particularly that on the west side of the street, later became
part of the huge housing project of the aetropolitan Life Isurance
Company.
April 10, 1938
P. L. Sperr
